
Switches:

	tarsius.localdir    > path to an alternate location for the local directory
	tarsius.gallery     > path to a gallery to open on startup
	tarsius.locale      > override the locale
	tarsius.thumbsclass > override the implementation for the thumbs permanent cache
 
External dependencies
 
	whirlycache
	concurrent (required by whirlycache)
		

A short checklist of stuff to look after when developing a GUI

 * mnemonics/shortcuts
 * internationalization and spacing: some languages need more room than others
 * growing/shrinking behavior
 